content: I'm so excited to try out the Studio Tour and learn more about the filmmaking process. I've heard that it's a really unique behind-the-scenes look at how movies and TV shows are made. Since I have an annual pass, I'll definitely be taking the tour multiple times to explore different parts of the studio each time. And speaking of annual passes, I'm also planning to visit other theme parks in the area, like Knott's Berry Farm and Disneyland. I've already been to Knott's Berry Farm a few times and had a great time, but I'm excited to explore more of the park and try out some new attractions.
